    "It can contain all data mentioned above and data beyond that.",
    "Examples include automatic identification system (AIS) data provided by the port authority (Sarabia-Jacome et al. 2020) or information for the tracking and monitoring of containers throughout the supply chain (Rajput and Singh 2018).",
